                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">Pupilfirst.com launched. Credit-integrated university programs (Apple, Facebook, Freshworks). Platform separated from brand.</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600"><strong>Business Model:</strong> B2B2C (corporate-funded university programs)</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600"><strong>Tech:</strong> LMS comparable to $100M+ platforms, open-sourced</p>
              </div>
