              </div>
              <div class="bg-white border-2 border-pink-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-pink-600 mb-1">The Second Design</p>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Pedagogy Testing + RealWorldReady</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">Vision divergence led to new path. HowToCBC → The Second Design. Education design studio. RealWorldReady program: 1,500+ learners, 63% rated 10/10.</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600"><strong>Focus:</strong> Agency-building, systems thinking, practice-heavy</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600"><strong>Clients:</strong> Colleges, nonprofits, businesses</p>
