                <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">"LITE is a failure—stop it." Shift from B2B2C to direct-to-consumer. Integration with Academic Bank of Credits (ABC). ₹999/month pricing.</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600"><strong>Business Model:</strong> Subscription-based D2C</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600"><strong>Strategy:</strong> Unbundle degrees, offer credit stacking</p>
