                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">EduMyna: The Integration</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-200 mb-3">All learnings converge. Pupilfirst LMS + The Second Design pedagogy + AI-first delivery. Automated grading, personalized paths, 24/7 AI assistants. Infrastructure + curriculum + scale.</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-300"><strong>Mission:</strong> Enable millions through AI-augmented education</p>
